book:
ODBC (Unified) ODBC
&reftitle.intro;
The ODBC extension allows you to use ODBC database drivers from PHP, using the same functions in PHP for any driver.
The following drivers and driver managers have direct support: IBM DB2, iODBC, and unixODBC.
It is strongly recommended to use a driver manager like iODBC or unixODBC with PHP. While you can use a driver directly with the ODBC extension through building against it directly, a driver manager provides better flexibility and compatibility. On Windows, the system driver manager is always used.
